Package edu.osu.cse.mmxi.machine.memory

Interface Summary
Memory A representation of random access memory within a hardware computer system.
 

Class Summary
FillMemory An implementation of physical memory where all words in all pages are initialized to a particular fill value.
MemoryUtilities The MemoryUtilities class contains several methods of general-purpose use which are used throughout the program.
PagedMemory A representation of random access memory within a hardware computer system.
RandomizedMemory An implementation of physical memory where all words in all pages are initialized to random bytes instead of zeros.
